<p>In the image above, three blocks are stacked vertically. The blocks are at rest, and the bottom one rests on a flat plane, with gravity present.</p>

<p>What systems experience an interaction with block 2? Choose all that apply.</p>

<choiceresponse>
	<checkboxgroup direction="vertical">
		<choice correct="true" name="block1"><text>A system with just block 1</text></choice>
		<choice correct="false" name="block2"><text>A system with just block 2</text></choice>
		<choice correct="true" name="block3"><text>A system with just block 3</text></choice>
		<choice correct="false" name="block2_3"><text>A system with blocks 2 and 3</text></choice>
		<choice correct="false" name="block1_2"><text>A system with blocks 1 and 2</text></choice>
		<choice correct="false" name="all3"><text>A system with all three blocks</text></choice>
	</checkboxgroup>
</choiceresponse>

